==English==
===Etymology===
From {{L.}} [[#Latin|Gordium]], derived from Greek [[Γορδιον]] (Gordion), the capital city of ancient Phrygia
===Adjective===
'''Gordian'''

#Of or pertaining to [[Gordium]], capital of [[Phrygia]] (now [[Yassihüyük]] in [[Turkey]]).
#Of the [[Gordian knot]].
#[[twist|Twisted]]; [[convoluted]]; tied as a [[knot]].

